# System Orchestrator — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

**Layer 1 — System Orchestrator** ties together the output of the 12 preceding modules into a single [execute_query](file:///c:/HelioX/orchestrator/orchestrator.py#99-186) lifecycle. 

## Observability & Diagnostics

We built a context-manager based metrics tracker [QueryDiagnostics](file:///c:/HelioX/orchestrator/observability.py#16-58) inside [observability.py](file:///c:/HelioX/orchestrator/observability.py). It wraps each logical block and generates a comprehensive `diagnostics` JSON block on every request to track latency bottlenecks and LLM token usage across retrieval, workers, synthesis, and composition.

Example usage:
```python
with measure_stage(diag, "compose_answer"):
    final_answer = self.composer.generate(validated_sqo, adjudication_result)
```

## The 8-Step Pipeline ([orchestrator.py](file:///c:/HelioX/tests/test_orchestrator.py))

1. **Pipeline Analysis:** [QueryAnalyzer](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/analyzer.py#35-183) → `QueryValidationAgent`
2. **Mode Selection:** [ModeController](file:///c:/HelioX/orchestrator/mode_controller.py#17-82) 
3. **Hybrid Retrieval:** [HybridRetrievalEngine](file:///c:/HelioX/retrieval/engine.py#42-284)
4. **Multi-Agent Execution & Synthesis:** [WorkerPool](file:///c:/HelioX/workers/pool.py#33-282) → [CrossChunkSynthesizer](file:///c:/HelioX/synthesis/synthesizer.py#22-117) → [AdjudicationEngine](file:///c:/HelioX/adjudication/engine.py#30-278)
5. **Answer Composition:** [AnswerComposer](file:///c:/HelioX/composer/generator.py#32-161)
6. **Confidence Gate:** [ConfidenceEngine](file:///c:/HelioX/confidence/engine.py#41-139)
7. **Memory Persistence:** [RedisSessionStore](file:///c:/HelioX/memory/session_store.py#20-104)
8. **Delivery:** Packages all evidence, citations, constraints, and metrics into an [OrchestratorResponse](file:///c:/HelioX/orchestrator/orchestrator.py#36-70).

